name: Five nights at Inersloths(html)
description:
Keep a eye/cam on... them then you'll make the night, probably...

Freddy's is long gone, candy's could only handle it for a year and Yosie's rebranded into Inersloths but someone has to be cheap...

FnaI is a point and click survival horror game, made by me, Home made indie games! if there's any errors/bugs, please contact me/leave a review. Note: This is the html version so it may break but the exe will come and the html will no longer be updated...
